org.jgentleframework.integration.remoting.rmi.annotation
Annotation Type RmiExporting

@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface RmiExporting

This annotation provides all information about specified RMI service exporter in order to export RMI service.

Author:
LE QUOC CHUNG - mailto: skydunkpro@yahoo.com
See Also:
RmiBinding

serviceInterface

public abstract java.lang.Class<?> serviceInterface
Service interface.

autoCreateRegistry

public abstract boolean autoCreateRegistry
In case of true, the current container will automate create registry service basing on the specified registry port if it can not find corresponding registry service

Default value is true.

Default:
true

autorun

public abstract boolean autorun
In case of true, the RMI service will be automate exported when the configured data loading. Otherwise, if false, you must use RmiExecutor in order to export RMI service.

Default value is true.

Default:
true

rmiExporter

public abstract RmiExporterConfig rmiExporter
Specifies information about corresponding RmiExporter

Default:
@org.jgentleframework.integration.remoting.rmi.annotation.RmiExporterConfig

compressing

public abstract boolean compressing
Compressing support. If specify true, the data is transfered between client and server will be automate compressed .

Default value is false

Default:
false
